Text: You do realize that we were just pasting that over and over again, right?
lol...no, I didn't. Call me gullible, but you never know when Scientology might strike. Like when you're in the shower, or getting some coffee. Anyway, enjoy the video!

Btw, it's good to know people have an interest in this video. Imho most of us Americans have no idea how many fundamentalist fanatics of various sorts we have in this country. With the 2008 elections coming up we should all get to know our friendly domestic zealots (*cough* Huckabee *cough cough* Romney)
If we seed will we get scientologists picketing in front of our homes? lol, thanks for the vid!  This needs to get out!
